<paragraph blockId="2.[317,1270,612,850]" box="[382,888,612,638]" pageId="2" pageNumber="195">Habitat. Littoral zone of the Danube River.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[317,1270,612,850]" pageId="2" pageNumber="195">
Distribution. Only known from the 
<typeStatus box="[790,841,647,673]" pageId="2" pageNumber="195">type</typeStatus>
locality as yet. But it possibly will be dispersed by the current in most of the Bulgarian and Romanian Danube River sectors down to the Danube Delta.
</paragraph>
